dialogue.library_intro: The first Imperial Navy destroyer to be loaded with the powerful large-type 61cm torpedoes, Mutsuki! While I'm an old model, I gave it my all on the frontlines!
dialogue.secretary3: Are you that interested in me? Ehehe...
dialogue.secretaryidle: Nya~ Hey Admiral… Mutsuki is a little bit bored...
dialogue.wedding: In truth, I wanted the Commander to praise me, so Mutsuki did her very, very best.
dialogue.show_players_score: Seems like a letter has arrived.
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: I want to take a little rest.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new ship-model appearance! Ja ja~n!
dialogue.return_from_sortie: Informing that the strategy has completed!
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Everyone! Are you ready for the sortie~?
dialogue.night_attack: I have a main gun and torpedo!
dialogue.artillery_spotting: I have a main gun and torpedo!
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: I have a main gun and torpedo!
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: I have a main gun and torpedo!
dialogue.mvp: Praise Mutsuki more and more! I grow more when I get praised~ Ehehehehe~
dialogue.minor_damaged2: Ueh... Mutsuki, only has paper-like armor...
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Nya, If, if it's still at this stage, I can still fight...!
dialogue.sunk: At least, I served, a bit, nya...
dialogue.valentines_day_2015: Here, Admiral. Mutsuki offers you this chocolate! Ehehe, please do♪
dialogue.white_day_2015: Umm, I made some cookies for Kisaragi-chan & the Admiral.... Would you like to try some?~
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Oh? Second anniversary～? Admiral! Kisaragi-chan! It's the second anniversary!
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: Kisaragi-chan, there sure has been a lot of rain recently. Oh yeah! Let's make some teruteru-bouzu! One each for Kisaragi-chan and Mutsuki!
dialogue.midsummer_2015: Oh? You going for a dip in the water, Admiral? Mutsuki is coming too! Swimsuit, swimsuit!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Kisaragi-chan, it's Christmas! This cake is sweet and delicioush! Here, here~!
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: So fast nya~. It's already December nya~. Must do some cleaning with Kisaragi-chan. fuu...
dialogue.setsubun_2016: Oyo? It's Setsubun? It's Setsubun! Mutsuki is going to throw! Hyah!
